comment: Represents a partition that contains application packages.

methods.comment:
* Returns the name identifying the partition.
         * @see Partition

methods.name: public File getFolder()
methods.comment: Returns the canonical folder of the partition.

methods.comment: Returns the non-canonical folder of the partition.

methods.comment: Returns the canonical priv-app folder of the partition, if one exists.

methods.name: public File getOverlayFolder()
methods.comment: Returns the canonical overlay folder of the partition, if one exists.

methods.name: public boolean containsFile(@NonNull File file)
methods.comment: Returns whether the partition contains the specified file.
